About Me

   I am working as a permanent researcher ('Chargée de Recherche') at
   INRIA in Grenoble, France. As from October 2017, I am heading the new
   Elan team which is focussed on the numerical modeling of complex
   mechanical phenomena.
   For further information, please refer to my new homepage.
