Research

   keywords

   A computational cell biologist, I use computer and mathematical models
   to study intracellular dynamics; in particular:
     * the intracellular biochemical networks at work in synaptic
       plasticity and its modulation, especially by astrocytes.
     * the influence of space and molecular crowding in cell signaling and
       biochemistry.

   The list of my publications and access to the articles is available
   here.
   Trombine Lambda Jongleur

